OL,3,CCould the Birmingham Balti become
OL,4,CUNESCO protected?
OL,6,FIt involves a specially designed balti
OL,7,Fbowl, made of thin pressed carbon
OL,8,Fsteel which heats up quickly. It's
OL,9,Ftypically cooked using vegetable oil
OL,10,Finstead of ghee, and cooked quickly
OL,11,Fover a high flame.
OL,13,FAndy Munro was born and bred in the
OL,14,FBalti Triangle and has championed the
OL,15,Fdish for many years, even having
OL,16,Fwritten a book on it: 'The Balti: Its
OL,17,FBirth, Its Boom Years and Beyond'.
OL,19,FHe is part of the campaign calling for
OL,20,FUNESCO status and says it would make a
OL,21,Fdifference to the culture.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
