CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773169881
OL,3,CCould the Birmingham Balti become
OL,4,CUNESCO protected?
OL,6,F"It'll be important for (Birmingham's
OL,7,FBalti Triangle restaurants) to say 'we
OL,8,Fdo a proper balti'," he said.
OL,10,F"Because what I don't want to happen
OL,11,Fis that visitors come to Birmingham -
OL,12,Fwe get more and more visitors coming
OL,13,Fto this city - go to a restaurant, see
OL,14,Fbalti on the menu, have it and think,
OL,15,F'this is no big deal, it's like every
OL,16,Fother curry I've had before.'"
OL,18,FIf Andy and the rest of the
OL,19,Fcampaigners are successful, these
OL,20,Fauthentic cooking methods could be
OL,21,Fsafeguarded for years to come.
